title: Ebro In The Morning - Yung Bleu + Pet Theft
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/26. 

Ebro and the crew discuss the phenomena of stolen pets (51), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (29 & 54), and you find out who played themselves. 

GUEST Yung Bleu discusses Drake, the Underground scene, and much more! 

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.

ALSO - PODCAST SUMMER JAM TICKET WINNERS ARE ANNOUNCED.
